WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:04.760
The Barclays app.
How to make a transfer.

2
00:00:05.360 --> 00:00:07.880
Need to transfer money between
your accounts?

3
00:00:08.080 --> 00:00:11.480
No problem - it's easily done with the Barclays app.

4
00:00:11.680 --> 00:00:15.720
Log in, and choose,
'Pay & Transfer' from the bottom menu.

5
00:00:17.480 --> 00:00:20.120
Select 'Transfer between accounts'.

6
00:00:22.040 --> 00:00:24.840
Choose the account you want
to transfer the money from

7
00:00:26.280 --> 00:00:29.960
and then the account
you want to transfer money to.

8
00:00:33.200 --> 00:00:36.040
Enter the amount, a reference

9
00:00:36.240 --> 00:00:40.600
and choose when to have the money
transferred - now or on a particular date.

10
00:00:41.280 --> 00:00:43.040
Tap 'Confirm'.

11
00:00:45.200 --> 00:00:49.400
And after checking it over,
confirm the transfer, and you're done.

